  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the bruised lemongrass and cook for 2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the canned crushed tomatoes, vegetable broth, dried basil, dried oregano, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook, covered, for 20 minutes, until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Remove the lemongrass and discard.",
    "Serve the ragu hot on a tagliere, garnished with fresh basil leaves if desired."
  ],
